des:
What Came First is a super-simple trivia game where you have to guess which of two things are the oldest. Get that right and you get a shot at guessing the year it came into the world for extra kudos.

So, if you had: Sandwiches or The USA, the answer would be sandwiches, which were invented in 1762. The USA didn’t come along until 1776.

There are 19 What Came Firsts to solve for free, with an interesting little factoid following each one.

Enjoy!

Here are some things you can say!
--------------------------------------
"Alexa, open What Came First"
"Repeat question"
